name: No Proc Stat Restriction
author: Magisk Modules Alt Repo
README:
# NoProcStatRestriction

## Introduction

Google has prevented user apps from accessing `/proc/stat` since Android O [for security reasons](https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/37140047), and this module is intended to bypass this.

[More information(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Magisk-Modules-Alt-Repo/NoProcStatRestriction/HEAD/blog)](https://young-lord.github.io/posts/%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AEproc_stat)

READMEsummary: Google has prevented user apps from accessing /proc/stat since Android O for security reasons.
